elief that improve\nment of the position of agriculture may j\nplay an important role in bringing about\ngeneral business revival in 1931.\nBALTIMORE STOCKS.\nSpecial Dispatch to The Star.\nBALTIMORE. November I.\nSales. STOCKS Last sale\n25 Arundel Corporation S9V\u00ab\n350 Baltimore Trust Co 33 V\u00ab\n273 BlacK A Decker com 14\n1 C P Telephone Ealto ptd 115\n51 Consolidated Oas com 91 'j\n80 Consolidated Coal com 4\n103 Fidelity A Oner Fire Corp 30\n30 First National Bank 43\n10 Manufacturers Fin Co pfd 13\u2018.^\n60 Maryland Casualty Co 35\nSO Mtc Bond A- Title Corp com 10'j\n5 New Amsterdam Cas Co 30\n70 11 B Fidelity A Oueranty 33'ii\n20 Western Maryland Dairy pfd 92'\nBONDS.\n5000 Maryland Electric Rwr 91i9....\n1000 United Rwy Elec let dafsT.... SOti\n7000 United Ry Elec income 4a.... 30\nTHE EVENING STAR. WASHINGTON. D. 0\u201e SATURDAY, NOVEMBER T. 1930.\n-*Frev. 1930.\u2014. Stock and Sales-\nHigh. Low. Dividend Rate. Add 00. Open. High. Low. Close.\n14% 5 Interstate Equities.. 6 6 6 4% 4%\n46 33% Intel st Eq cv pf 3).. 1 34 34 34 34\n27 9% Irving Air Chute <1). 18% 8% 8% 8%\n18 4 Italian Superp A). 1 5 5 5 5\n19% 10 Klein (DE) Co (1)... 1 12% 12% 12% 12%\n4% Leonard Oil 2 1 1\n27 11% Libby McNeil L... 6 12 12 12 12\n20% 3% Loew\u2019s Inc war).... 16% 6% 6% 6%\n1 55% 23% Lone Star Gas n (1).. 9 24% 24% 24% 24%\n113% 107% Long Isl Ltpf (7)... 10a 110 110 110 110\n5 1 Louisiana Lan Ex. 2 1% 1% 1% 1%\n24% 10 MacMarr Stores (1). 1 10% 10% 10% 10%\n49% 37 Mapes C Mfg (13%). 1 38% 38% 38% 38%\n3% Mavis Bottling 19\n90 65% Mead Johnson (t 4%) 2 74% 74% 74% 74%\n22% 10% Memphis N O <t7oc>. 1 12% 12% 12% 12%\n16% Met Min Ino 0.20). 11% 1% 1% 1%\n11% 3% Mid St Pet vtc A 1 3 3 3 3\n6 1% MldSt Pet vtc 8.... 4 1% 1% 1% 1%\n38 20% Mid West Ut <b\u00df%)., 7 21% 21% 21% 21%\n27% 10 Miss Rlv Fuel bd rts. 1 12% 12% 12% 12%\n36% 7% Mo Kan P L <blo%). 2 9% 9% 9% 9%\n6 Mo Kan P L vtc. 2\n12% 5% Mount Prod (1.60)... 4.6 6% 6 6%\n27 10 Nachman Spring.... 19% 9% 9*4 9%\n12%